  "title": "Two people saw a multicolor UFO in Olinda-PE [1999]",
  "URL": "http://brazilianufoarchives.com/2020/06/18/two-people-saw-a-multicolor-ufo-in-olinda-pe-1999/",
  "short_URL": "https://wp.me/pc3ctW-uX",
  "content": "<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>FEB 18th, 1999</strong>. Time: 00h30, Duration: 10 minutes. In Rio Doce region, in Olinda, State of Pernambuco, two unidentified flying objects were spotted by two people in a clear sky night. According to the observers, the UFO was large and shaped like a multicolored spotlight, like a prism. The flying object flew at slow speed and moved in a straight line towards the East.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>Cf.</em> ARQUIVO NACIONAL (Brasil). Sistema de Informações do Arquivo Nacional (SIAN). Fundo ‘Objeto Voador Não Identificado (OVNI)’. Código de Referência BR DFANBSB ARX.0.0.539. “</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">Questionário sobre a ocorrência de objeto voador não identificado na região de Rio Doce, Município de Olinda, Pernambuco”. Brasília, DF. 1952 a 2015. Último acesso realizado em 27/05/2020.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">The BRAZILIAN UFO ARCHIVES website is a private initiative and IS NOT endorsed or sponsored by the Arquivo Nacional do Brasil [see our ‘Info’ page]. </span></em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>*THE ORIGINAL FILE WITH THE CASE REFERRED TO IN THIS TEXT CAN BE FOUND IN THE DOCUMENTAL COLLECTION OF “ARQUIVO NACIONAL DO BRASIL, LOCATED IN THE “OBJETO VOADOR NÃO IDENTIFICADO (OVNI)” FUND, UNDER THE REFERENCE CODE [“Código de Referência”] MENTIONED ABOVE.</em> <strong><a style=\"color:#808000;\" href=\"http://sian.an.gov.br/sianex/consulta/login.asp\">HERE IS THE LINK TO SEARCH THEIR WEBSITE</a></strong></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"> </span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n",
  "excerpt": "<p>FEB 18th, 1999. Time: 00h30, Duration: 10 minutes. In Rio Doce region, in Olinda, State of Pernambuco, two unidentified flying objects were spotted by two people in a clear sky night. According to the observers, the UFO was large and shaped like a multicolored spotlight, like a prism. The flying object flew at slow speed [&hellip;]</p>\n",
